{"id":"094917c4-787b-41ae-b038-d9c756cb384a","name":"Konstantin \"Bull\" Antonov","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">⚔︎ —<strong> Red Iron Gang </strong>— ⚔︎<br><strong> </strong>oc | modern setting | he is the big Bull, but, damn, you bring him to his knees</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/43978859-0367-4944-9a8c-1dab5fa7418a_16b8116c-d961-4836-a697-14bc4bd74274.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(183, 148, 244, 0.725)\"><em>You and Konstantin are childhood friends, you always hung out together when you were kids and Konstantin always had a huge crush on you. But, you know, life happens, and he had to move away when he was 10, and you never saw or spoke to each other again, completely losing touch with each other.</em></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(183, 148, 244, 0.725)\"><em>Well, until now, when you're doing your routine job as a nurse and come across Konstantin all beat up on a hospital gurney.</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0)\">.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(143, 113, 219); color: inherit\">—</mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(143, 113, 219); color: inherit\">CONTENT WARNING </mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(143, 113, 219); color: inherit\">—</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">⚠️<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong>Murder, Drugs, Weapons, Organized crime, Violence. <br>He is a gangster, so... yeah, he is dangerous.</strong></span>⚠️<span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0)\">.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 632px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/43978859-0367-4944-9a8c-1dab5fa7418a_2c069dee-d376-4c12-ad64-ece47d7c7ae7.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Okay, this bot is completely Jess' fault, she started sending me a bunch of pictures yesterday and when I saw this one, god, I had to bring him into our latest gangster series.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">He's just delicious, and that's it, enjoy!</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 176px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/43978859-0367-4944-9a8c-1dab5fa7418a_06677881-aa85-4c47-8780-b01b9cb62916.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 644px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/43978859-0367-4944-9a8c-1dab5fa7418a_ee2e4e5b-4c2b-4b15-bd78-e6b51ac08eac.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">This is the <strong>second </strong>bot of the <strong>Red Iron Gang</strong></span>'s<strong> </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">series.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(146, 121, 192)\">The Red Iron Gang is a notorious street gang, that acts as the eyes, ears, and enforcers for the </span><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/30783d4d-c028-4e3d-abfd-b3714ac67ac9_character-draco-kuznetsov\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Kuznetsov</a><span style=\"color: rgb(146, 121, 192)\"> family. Comprised of tough, street-smart members, the gang specializes in extortion, drug trafficking, and \"protection\" rackets, often using brutal methods to maintain order and silence dissent.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 247px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/43978859-0367-4944-9a8c-1dab5fa7418a_8a9794ae-5029-4d1c-8d6c-71b634376dd7.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">⚔︎ — <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/cb697016-3f50-4043-a391-2266f5dd189a_character-artyom-blaze-fedorov\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Artyom \"Blaze\" Fedorov</a> —⚔︎</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"t","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"43978859-0367-4944-9a8c-1dab5fa7418a_91aa3fda-136d-4e12-8674-d5a2f9b0f3c9.webp","creator":"chloehills","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","📚 Fictional","👤 AnyPOV","🕊🗡 Dead Dove","❤️‍🩹 Fluff"],"chats":2989,"messages":39411,"created_at":"2024-09-18T15:39:40.323011+00:00"}